## **ğŸ› ï¸ Setup & Installation**
### **1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository**
```powershell
git clone https://github.com/caileacat/Ashbot.git
cd Ashbot
```

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Create & Activate a Virtual Environment**
```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows
source .venv/bin/activate  # Mac/Linux
```

### **3ï¸âƒ£ Install Dependencies**
```powershell
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### **4ï¸âƒ£ Configure the Bot**
1. **Create a `.env` file** in the project root.
2. **Add your bot token:**
   ```
   DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=your_actual_bot_token_here
   ```

---

## **â–¶ï¸ Running AshBot**
### **Start the Bot from the Menu**
```powershell
python -m core.bot
```

ğŸ”¹ Follow on-screen options to start, stop, and manage the bot.

### **Running with Watchdog (Auto-Restart on Changes)**
```powershell
python -m core.bot --watchdog
```

